00:35:23,880 --> 00:35:26,520
 If you do not repent, Jesus said,

656
00:35:26,520 --> 00:35:30,520
 "I'll come to you and remove you from the lamb stand.

657
00:35:30,520 --> 00:35:33,560
 "You're no longer my people.

