00:39:52,960 --> 00:39:57,120
 Help us to taste your grace and your love once again.

726
00:39:57,120 --> 00:39:58,880
 Anew.

727
00:39:58,880 --> 00:40:01,480
 Renew our spirit,

728
00:40:01,480 --> 00:40:04,980
 so that we can be your faithful followers.

